            <span class="text-4xl font-mono-numbers font-bold text-[#7af28c] block">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">PRECISION</h4>
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3" style="isolation: isolate;">
                <span class="text-highlight-purple whitespace-nowrap">Hallucination-Resistant Architecture.</span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3" style="isolation: isolate;">
                Generative AI in the enterprise fails without a <span class="text-highlight-purple whitespace-nowrap">"Source of Truth."</span> We bring Big Tech rigor to the mid-market, building resilient Context Layers <span class="text-highlight-purple whitespace-nowrap">(RAG Architectures)</span> that ground your AI agents in proprietary facts, not generic training data. We turn "prompts" into reliable business processes.
