        <div class="glass p-4 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[rgb(var(--color-secondary))]/30 transition-all duration-300 reveal reveal-7">
          <!-- Mobile: Vertical Stack -->
          <div class="md:hidden space-y-3">
            <span class="text-4xl font-mono-numbers font-bold text-[#7af28c] block">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">AGNOSTICISM</h4>
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3" style="isolation: isolate;">
                <span class="text-highlight-purple whitespace-nowrap">Vendor-Neutral Liquidity.</span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3" style="isolation: isolate;">
                We do not resell software. We do not lock you into a <span class="text-highlight-purple whitespace-nowrap">"Black Box"</span> platform. We build an open, flexible data architecture that allows you to plug in any AI model (OpenAI, Anthropic, Llama) today or tomorrow. We build for the <span class="text-highlight-purple whitespace-nowrap">Exit Story</span> -ensuring the technology stack is a transferable asset the next buyer pays a premium for.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 italic">
                The Impact: No "Vendor Debt." You own the IP. You own the architecture.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
